  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis as Type 2 Diabetes

          -  Patients who have been placed on dietary therapy/exercise therapy, without achievement
             of glycemic control

          -  Outpatients

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 1 diabetes mellitus, diabetes that is a result of pancreatic injury, or secondary
             forms of diabetes

          -  Significant heart diseases

          -  Significant diabetic complications

        Other protocol-defined inclusion/exclusion criteria may apply
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
